      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋太宗、赵德芳、杨继业同上。宋太宗（念）眼观旌旂起，",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00002",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "耳听好消息。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00003",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "老将军沙滩赴会，受惊了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00004",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "主公但放宽心，众孩儿回来，便知明白。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00005",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨延德、杨延昭、杨延嗣同上。杨延嗣（同白）主公在上，臣等班师回来。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00006",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "有劳众位将军。杨延嗣（同白）爹爹在上，孩儿拜揖。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00007",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。你等回来了？杨延嗣（同白）回来了。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00008",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "大哥呢？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00009",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "大哥长枪刺死。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00010",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "二哥呢？杨延嗣（同白）二哥短剑身亡。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00011",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "三哥呢？杨延嗣（同白）三哥马踏如泥。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00012",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "四郎呢？杨延嗣（同白）四哥失落在番邦。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00013",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00014",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "失落番邦。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00015",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！（唱）听罢言来我的魂飘荡，（白）哎呀，苍天吓。（唱）好一似利刃穿胸心痛伤。杨大郎长枪阵前丧，二郎短剑把身亡。我三郎马踏为肉酱，四郎失落在番邦。",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00016",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "这一阵吓破了王的胆，可叹杨家众儿男。老将军休得把孤怨，朕封你官上加职，职上加官。杨继业",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00017",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "老臣亦非嫌官小，保国忠良无下梢。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00018",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "杨大郎身替孤王死，朕封他龙华会上神。杨二郎短剑伤了命，朕封他花花太岁神。杨三郎马踏为肉酱，朕封他逍遥快活神。四郎失落无音信，在生封官，死后封神。杨继业",
      "text_length": 75
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00019",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "叩头三呼把龙恩谢，回头来看见众儿郎。六郎儿在旁双流泪，杨七郎一旁泪汪汪。五郎哭的如酒醉，忽然想起你们的娘。送出我父子府门外，手扯袍铠暗神伤：天波府交与你八员将，回朝来还我人四双。弟兄们为国把命丧，拿甚么交还你的娘？宋太宗",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00020",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "开言就把七郎叫，五郎、六郎听朕封：杨六郎朕封你三关为总镇，杨七郎朕封你火龙大将军。五郎别的官儿不封你，封你在朝并肩王。杨延德",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00021",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "杨五郎跪尘埃泪双流，想起保国的忠良没有下场头。大哥身替宋王死，二哥短剑把身亡；三哥马踏为肉酱，四哥失落在番邦。今日杀来明日杀，杀来杀去杀自家。刀刀割去心上肉，箭箭射的白莲花。杨五郎解破其中意，要把这金刀削头发。在上面辞别万岁爷的驾，（白）哎呀，万岁爷呀！（唱）臣要到五台去出家。",
      "text_length": 139
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00022",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "五将军说的哪里话，说甚么五台去出家。你不念父母年高大，忍心去了头上发。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00023",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延德"
      ],
      "text": "昔日里庄王求莲华，相遇一女貌如花。她不愿皇宫招驸马，百雀寺里去出家。父王劝她心不转，到后来功德圆满作菩萨。为臣辞别了贤王驾，臣要到五台去出家。",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00024",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "赵德芳"
      ],
      "text": "五将军说话理太差，说什么五台去出家。叔王江山全仗你，保驾回朝把官加。杨延德",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00025",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "赵德芳"
      ],
      "text": "打罢春来又复秋，夕阳桥下水东流。自古多少忠良将，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00026",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00027",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "唱杨继业",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00028",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
