    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00031",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "",
      "text_length": 0
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00032",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "唱哪一个为国能到头？在一旁辞别了年迈的父，哎！儿要到五台去把禅修。𠳶！骂一声五郎没来由，说什么五台把禅修。六郎他还年纪幼，七郎他还是小娃娃。父子们辞别了宋王爷的驾，回到火塘寨上作田家。别下了为父倒还罢，天波府哭坏了你的妈。老将军舍了罢。哎呀，万岁。老臣八个孩儿，到幽州赴会，只剩得六郎、七郎，五郎又要出家，叫老臣难以割舍。为父的带领你兄弟八个，犹如那八只虎闯到边关。赴番邦双龙会替王假扮，死的死走的走三儿命还。延昭儿延嗣儿年幼识浅，延德儿为甚么又去修禅？你来看为父的天可怜鉴，好比那风前烛瓦上霜能过几年？既出家随为父保驾回转，见过你老娘亲再了尘缘。（白）哎呀，我的儿吓！杨延德",
      "text_length": 288
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00033",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "汉朝有个张子房，求仙修道细参详。孩儿心内俱参破，忠臣良将无下场。老爹爹不必泪双降，儿在五台渡慈航。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00034",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "长老上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00035",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "长老"
      ],
      "text": "五台山，众僧伺候了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00036",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众僧人"
      ],
      "text": "哦。宋太宗（白）五台山寺主。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00037",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "长老"
      ],
      "text": "贫僧在。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00038",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "听孤王旨意：五将军，乃是寡人的爱卿，五台山出家，孤王回朝，发库银五十万，以为功课，金刀落发。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00039",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "长老"
      ],
      "text": "贫僧领旨。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00040",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "五将军出家，受寡人一拜。杨延嗣（同白）又道君不拜臣。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00041",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业",
        "杨延昭",
        "赵德芳"
      ],
      "text": "小王也有一拜。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00042",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业",
        "杨延昭",
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "大不拜小。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00043",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "延德儿，为父也有一拜。杨延嗣（同白）父不拜子。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00044",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "六郎，七郎，你们手足之情，多拜几拜。杨延嗣（同白）孩儿知道。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00045",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨延昭、杨延嗣同拜。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00046",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "请驾回宫。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00047",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋太宗"
      ],
      "text": "摆驾。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00048",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵德芳"
      ],
      "text": "咦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00049",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋太宗、赵德芳同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00050",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹请转回，到天波府，拜上年迈娘亲，恕孩儿不孝之罪。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00051",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "五郎，延德，还记得你的娘亲？若是舍不得母亲，可随为父回去，到天波府，见过你年迈母亲，再来出家也罢。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00052",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "自古道出家容易还家难，孩儿有万死之罪。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00053",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "哎儿吓！（唱）大海孤舟折了桅，断线风筝不得回，燕子衔泥空费力，长大毛羽各自飞。（三叫头）五郎！延德！哎，难得见的儿吓！（白）六郎，七郎。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00054",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭",
        "杨延嗣"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00055",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "随为父这里来。杨延嗣",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00056",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00057",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨延昭",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "哎哎！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008040_e00058",
      "play_id": "02008040",
      "scene_id": "02008040_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
